These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, soy-milk
3 different games are played: chess, bridge, snooker
1. the person playing bridge is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person playing snooker and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | soy-milk | juice |
| Game   | bridge     | chess    | snooker   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, sudoku
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, taxi, trike
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the van and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | drawing    | sudoku        | rock-climbing |
| Transport     | taxi | trike | van         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, tea
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, mystery, adventure
1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the person watching mystery movies and the person drinking tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | mirinda | cola     | tea |
| Movie-Genre        | mystery  | adventure | family |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, old-henry, cain
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goldfish
1. the bolivar-smoker is the owner of the bird##1
2. the cain-smoker is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the bird##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Cigar   | old-henry  | cain     | bolivar |
| Pet           | fish | goldfish | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
3 different games are played: poker, scrabble, canasta
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, goat
1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing poker##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Game   | scrabble | canasta     | poker |
| Pet     | goat    | chinchilla | fish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, indian
House: cape-cod, farmhouse, victorian
1. the cape-cod house is between the indian and the dutch##2
2. the dutch is the farmhouse house##1
3. the egyptian is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | dutch  | egyptian   | indian        |
| House         | farmhouse | cape-cod | victorian |

