.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, satire, western
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, parkour, volleyball
1. the person watching satire movies is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching western movies##2
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | comedy  | satire  |
| Sport   | rowing | parkour | volleyball |

