The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Hobby       | woodworking | camping | cooking  |
| Transport   | snowmobile    | bus        | quad-bike |

