.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, social-worker
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, orchid, daffodil
1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the social-worker##1
2. the lawyer is between the person who growsdaffodil and the fisherman##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Job         | social-worker | lawyer | fisherman |
| Flower   | daffodil     | tulip    | orchid |

