2. the montecristo-smoker is between the tiparillo-smoker and the davidoff-smoker##2
3. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | rock   | salsa   |
| Cigar         | davidoff | montecristo | tiparillo |

