2. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person drinking fanta and the person traveling to liverpool##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2   |   3    |
| Beverage   | fanta  | 7up   | juice  |
| City        | hannover | hamburg | liverpool |

