.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, train, snowmobile
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, gospel, punk
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the person driving the train is between the person driving the snowmobile and the fan of gospel##2
3. the fan of disco is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Transport      | snowmobile | train   | quad-bike |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | disco | gospel   |

 